@DATABASE "Super G-Man"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Super G-Man"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                                Super G-Man
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(31936,0)"}          31936,0
@{"Infinite Ammo " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28118,0)"}          28118,0
@{"Infinite Fuel " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28564,0)"}          28564,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(30786,255)"}          30786,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
